### Variables
@host = http://localhost:8080
@phoneA = +33611111111
@phoneB = +33622222222

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### SETUP — Créer les utilisateurs
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 1. Register user A
POST {{host}}/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "Lucas",
  "password": "test123",
  "phoneNumber": "{{phoneA}}",
  "email": "lucas.msg@test.com"
}

### 2. Register user B
POST {{host}}/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "Camille",
  "password": "test123",
  "phoneNumber": "{{phoneB}}",
  "email": "camille.msg@test.com"
}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### SETUP — Login
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 3. Login as Lucas
POST {{host}}/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "{{phoneA}}",
  "password": "test123"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("token", response.body.trim().replace(/^"|"$/g, ""));
%}

### 4. Login as Camille
POST {{host}}/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "{{phoneB}}",
  "password": "test123"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("tokenB", response.body.trim().replace(/^"|"$/g, ""));
%}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### SETUP — Friendship (la conv DIRECT est créée à l'acceptation)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 5. Lucas envoie une demande d'ami à Camille
POST {{host}}/api/friendships
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "phoneNumber": "{{phoneB}}"
}

### 6. Camille récupère ses demandes reçues (capture friendshipId)
GET {{host}}/api/friendships/received
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenB}}

> {%
    client.global.set("friendshipId", response.body[0].id);
%}

### 7. Camille accepte la demande (crée la conv DIRECT automatiquement)
POST {{host}}/api/friendships/{{friendshipId}}/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenB}}

### 8. Lucas récupère ses conversations pour attraper le conversationId
GET {{host}}/api/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

> {%
    client.global.set("conversationId", response.body[0].conversationId);
%}


### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### ENVOI DE MESSAGES
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 9. Lucas envoie un message à Camille (expects 201)
POST {{host}}/api/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="conversationId"

{{conversationId}}
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="content"

Salut Camille !
--WebAppBoundary--

### 10. Camille répond à Lucas (expects 201 — même conversationId)
POST {{host}}/api/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenB}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="conversationId"

{{conversationId}}
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="content"

Salut Lucas, ça va ?
--WebAppBoundary--

### 11. Lucas lit les messages de la conversation (expects 200 avec 2 messages)
GET {{host}}/api/messages/conversation/{{conversationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### CAS LIMITES
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

